channel.title: Flog It!
channel.desc: Paul Martin is at the Watts Gallery in the heart of the Surrey countryside with experts David Harper and Thomas Plant. David uncovers a collection of British film and TV memorabilia and Thomas is thrilled by some French cameo glass. Also, Paul Martin is on the trail of martians in Woking: the setting for HG Wells's sci-fi novel `The War Of The Worlds'.
